Package civitas.celestis.math.complex

Class Complex

java.lang.Object
civitas.celestis.math.vector.Vector2
civitas.celestis.math.complex.Complex
All Implemented Interfaces:
Numeric, Vector, Serializable, Comparable<Vector2>
public class Complex extends Vector2 implements Comparable<Vector2>
A complex number: x + yi

The component x represents the real part of this number, and the component y represents the imaginary part of this number.
